  <brief_title>Effect of Topical Trimebutine on Pain After Hemorrhoidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Trimebutine on Postoperative Pain After Milligan-Morgan Hemorrhoidectomy: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
